<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Install PaperTrail</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif; max-width: 42rem; margin: 3rem auto; padding: 0 1rem; line-height: 1.5; }
      .card { border: 1px solid #d0d7de; border-radius: 16px; padding: 1.25rem; }
      a.button { display: inline-block; background: #0a84ff; color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 0.8rem 1.1rem; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: 600; }
      code { background: #f6f8fa; padding: 0.15rem 0.35rem; border-radius: 6px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="card">
      <h1>Install PaperTrail</h1>
      <p>This build is signed for Ad Hoc distribution. The iPhone or iPad must already be registered in the provisioning profile.</p>
      <p><a class="button" href="itms-services://?action=download-manifest&amp;url=https://github.com/${{ github.repository }}/releases/download/adhoc-latest/manifest.plist">Install on iPhone or iPad</a></p>
      <p>If install fails, check that:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>the device UDID is in the Ad Hoc profile</li>
        <li>the app was signed with the matching Apple Distribution certificate</li>
        <li>the release assets are publicly reachable</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Direct IPA URL: <code>${IPA_URL}</code></p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
